---
// Visual Process Timeline - Enhanced from Dry Main's visual approach
---

<section class="py-16 bg-white" id="visual-process-timeline">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto">
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-4 uppercase">
          Our 6-Step Process
        </h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-slate-600 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
          From inspection to warranty, we handle every detail including permits, inspections, and subsidy paperwork
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Visual Timeline Bar (Desktop) -->
      <div class="hidden lg:block mb-16">
        <div class="relative">
          <!-- Connection Line -->
          <div class="absolute top-1/2 left-0 right-0 h-1 bg-amber-300 -translate-y-1/2"></div>
          
          <!-- Timeline Steps -->
          <div class="flex justify-between relative">
            <div class="flex flex-col items-center">
              <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-amber-500 text-black rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-xl relative z-10 border-4 border-white shadow-lg">
                1
              </div>
              <span class="text-xs text-slate-500 mt-2 font-semibold">1-2 hours</span>
              <span class="text-sm font-bold text-slate-900 mt-1">Inspection</span>
            </div>
            
            <div class="flex flex-col items-center">
              <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-amber-500 text-black rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-xl relative z-10 border-4 border-white shadow-lg">
                2
              </div>
              <span class="text-xs text-slate-500 mt-2 font-semibold">Same day</span>
              <span class="text-sm font-bold text-slate-900 mt-1">Planning</span>
            </div>
            
            <div class="flex flex-col items-center">
              <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-amber-500 text-black rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-xl relative z-10 border-4 border-white shadow-lg">
                3
              </div>
              <span class="text-xs text-slate-500 mt-2 font-semibold">2-7 days</span>
              <span class="text-sm font-bold text-slate-900 mt-1">Installation</span>
            </div>
            
            <div class="flex flex-col items-center">
              <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-amber-500 text-black rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-xl relative z-10 border-4 border-white shadow-lg">
                4
              </div>
              <span class="text-xs text-slate-500 mt-2 font-semibold">~2 business days</span>
              <span class="text-sm font-bold text-slate-900 mt-1">Inspection</span>
            </div>
            
            <div class="flex flex-col items-center">
              <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-amber-500 text-black rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-xl relative z-10 border-4 border-white shadow-lg">
                5
              </div>
              <span class="text-xs text-slate-500 mt-2 font-semibold">1 day</span>
              <span class="text-sm font-bold text-slate-900 mt-1">Restoration</span>
            </div>
            
            <div class="flex flex-col items-center">
              <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-amber-500 text-black rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-xl relative z-10 border-4 border-white shadow-lg">
                6
              </div>
              <span class="text-xs text-slate-500 mt-2 font-semibold">Same day</span>
              <span class="text-sm font-bold text-slate-900 mt-1">Close-Out</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Process Cards with Time Badges -->
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
        <!-- Step 1 -->
        <div class="bg-white border-2 border-slate-200 overflow-hidden hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow">
          <div class="relative h-48">
            <img 
              alt="Free Professional Inspection" 
              class="w-full h-full object-cover" width="600" height="400" decoding="async" 
              loading="lazy" 
              src="/images/waterproofing/basement-water-leak-inspection.webp"
            />
            <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-black/60 to-transparent"></div>
            <div class="absolute top-3 left-3">
              <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-amber-500 text-black rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-lg border-2 border-white">
                1
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="absolute bottom-3 right-3">
              <span class="bg-black/80 text-white text-xs px-3 py-1 rounded font-semibold">
                1-2 HOURS
              </span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="p-5">
            <h3 class="font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2 uppercase">Free Inspection & Diagnostics</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-slate-600">
              Comprehensive moisture mapping, drain camera inspection, foundation assessment. 
              We identify all water entry points and provide solutions.
            </p>
            <div class="mt-3 pt-3 border-t border-slate-100">
              <ul class="text-xs text-slate-500 space-y-1">
                <li>✓ Digital moisture detection</li>
                <li>✓ Camera inspection if needed</li>
                <li>✓ Written assessment report</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Step 2 -->
        <div class="bg-white border-2 border-slate-200 overflow-hidden hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow">
          <div class="relative h-48">
            <img 
              alt="Compliance and Planning" 
              class="w-full h-full object-cover" width="600" height="400" decoding="async" 
              loading="lazy" 
              src="/images/waterproofing/building-permit.webp"
            />
            <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-black/60 to-transparent"></div>
            <div class="absolute top-3 left-3">
              <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-amber-500 text-black rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-lg border-2 border-white">
                2
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="absolute bottom-3 right-3">
              <span class="bg-black/80 text-white text-xs px-3 py-1 rounded font-semibold">
                SAME DAY
              </span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="p-5">
            <h3 class="font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2 uppercase">Plan & Compliance</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-slate-600">
              Choose interior/exterior approach, confirm Ontario One Call locates, 
              prepare permits and City of Toronto subsidy paperwork.
            </p>
            <div class="mt-3 pt-3 border-t border-slate-100">
              <ul class="text-xs text-slate-500 space-y-1">
                <li>✓ Permit applications submitted</li>
                <li>✓ Subsidy eligibility confirmed</li>
                <li>✓ Ontario One Call initiated</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Step 3 -->
        <div class="bg-white border-2 border-slate-200 overflow-hidden hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow">
          <div class="relative h-48">
            <img 
              alt="Professional Installation" 
              class="w-full h-full object-cover" width="600" height="400" decoding="async" 
              loading="lazy" 
              src="/images/waterproofing/exterior-waterproofing-toronto in process (1).webp"
            />
            <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-black/60 to-transparent"></div>
            <div class="absolute top-3 left-3">
              <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-amber-500 text-black rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-lg border-2 border-white">
                3
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="absolute bottom-3 right-3">
              <span class="bg-black/80 text-white text-xs px-3 py-1 rounded font-semibold">
                2-7 DAYS
              </span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="p-5">
            <h3 class="font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2 uppercase">Professional Installation</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-slate-600">
              Sequential work: excavation, membrane/drainage installation, sump systems, 
              backwater valves. WSIB-cleared crews following OHSA guidelines.
            </p>
            <div class="mt-3 pt-3 border-t border-slate-100">
              <ul class="text-xs text-slate-500 space-y-1">
                <li>✓ Daily progress photos</li>
                <li>✓ Safety protocols followed</li>
                <li>✓ Minimal disruption</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Step 4 -->
        <div class="bg-white border-2 border-slate-200 overflow-hidden hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow">
          <div class="relative h-48">
            <img 
              alt="City Inspection" 
              class="w-full h-full object-cover" width="600" height="400" decoding="async" 
              loading="lazy" 
              src="/images/waterproofing/sump pump with water.webp"
            />
            <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-black/60 to-transparent"></div>
            <div class="absolute top-3 left-3">
              <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-amber-500 text-black rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-lg border-2 border-white">
                4
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="absolute bottom-3 right-3">
              <span class="bg-black/80 text-white text-xs px-3 py-1 rounded font-semibold">
                ~2 BUSINESS DAYS
              </span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="p-5">
            <h3 class="font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2 uppercase">Code & City Inspections</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-slate-600">
              Book inspections, ensure sump discharge ≥2m from foundation per By-law 681, 
              verify full-port backwater valve installation.
            </p>
            <div class="mt-3 pt-3 border-t border-slate-100">
              <ul class="text-xs text-slate-500 space-y-1">
                <li>✓ Inspector coordination</li>
                <li>✓ Code compliance verified</li>
                <li>✓ Subsidy approval confirmed</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Step 5 -->
        <div class="bg-white border-2 border-slate-200 overflow-hidden hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow">
          <div class="relative h-48">
            <img 
              alt="Site Restoration" 
              class="w-full h-full object-cover" width="600" height="400" decoding="async" 
              loading="lazy" 
              src="/images/waterproofing/basement_wall_insulation.webp"
            />
            <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-black/60 to-transparent"></div>
            <div class="absolute top-3 left-3">
              <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-amber-500 text-black rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-lg border-2 border-white">
                5
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="absolute bottom-3 right-3">
              <span class="bg-black/80 text-white text-xs px-3 py-1 rounded font-semibold">
                1 DAY
              </span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="p-5">
            <h3 class="font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2 uppercase">Restore & Clean</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-slate-600">
              Replace concrete, restore landscaping, complete interior finishes. 
              Your property returned to better-than-before condition.
            </p>
            <div class="mt-3 pt-3 border-t border-slate-100">
              <ul class="text-xs text-slate-500 space-y-1">
                <li>✓ Professional concrete work</li>
                <li>✓ Landscaping restoration</li>
                <li>✓ Complete site cleanup</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Step 6 -->
        <div class="bg-white border-2 border-slate-200 overflow-hidden hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow">
          <div class="relative h-48">
            <img 
              alt="Project Close-Out" 
              class="w-full h-full object-cover" width="600" height="400" decoding="async" 
              loading="lazy" 
              src="/images/waterproofing/dryspace_excellence.webp"
            />
            <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-black/60 to-transparent"></div>
            <div class="absolute top-3 left-3">
              <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-amber-500 text-black rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-lg border-2 border-white">
                6
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="absolute bottom-3 right-3">
              <span class="bg-black/80 text-white text-xs px-3 py-1 rounded font-semibold">
                SAME DAY
              </span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="p-5">
            <h3 class="font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2 uppercase">Final Close-Out</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-slate-600">
              Final inspection booked, WSIB clearance certificate provided, 
              complete photo documentation and warranty registration.
            </p>
            <div class="mt-3 pt-3 border-t border-slate-100">
              <ul class="text-xs text-slate-500 space-y-1">
                <li>✓ Permit closure completed</li>
                <li>✓ Documentation package</li>
                <li>✓ 25-year warranty activated</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Process Benefits -->
      <div class="mt-12 bg-slate-50 border-2 border-slate-200 p-8">
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-6 text-center uppercase">
          What Sets Our Process Apart
        </h3>
        
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-4 gap-4">
          <div class="text-center">
            <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-amber-50 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-3">
              <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-amber-500" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h4 class="font-bold text-sm text-slate-900 mb-1 uppercase">Digital Documentation</h4>
            <p class="text-xs text-slate-500">Every step photographed and documented</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="text-center">
            <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-cyan-50 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-3">
              <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-cyan-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12h6m-6 4h6m2 5H7a2 2 0 01-2-2V5a2 2 0 012-2h5.586a1 1 0 01.707.293l5.414 5.414a1 1 0 01.293.707V19a2 2 0 01-2 2z"></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h4 class="font-bold text-sm text-slate-900 mb-1 uppercase">WSIB-Cleared Teams</h4>
            <p class="text-xs text-slate-500">Licensed, insured professionals</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="text-center">
            <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-cyan-50 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-3">
              <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-cyan-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 20h5v-2a3 3 0 00-5.356-1.857M17 20H7m10 0v-2c0-.656-.126-1.283-.356-1.857M7 20H2v-2a3 3 0 015.356-1.857M7 20v-2c0-.656.126-1.283.356-1.857m0 0a5.002 5.002 0 019.288 0M15 7a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0zm6 3a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0zM7 10a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0z"></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h4 class="font-bold text-sm text-slate-900 mb-1 uppercase">Dedicated PM</h4>
            <p class="text-xs text-slate-500">Single point of contact throughout</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="text-center">
            <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-red-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-3">
              <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-red-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 8v4l3 3m6-3a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h4 class="font-bold text-sm text-slate-900 mb-1 uppercase">On-Time Guarantee</h4>
            <p class="text-xs text-slate-500">We meet our timelines or discount applies</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>